LITTLE SECRETS
By Stephen Sviatko

A simple short message encryption system that uses the cryptography features of the SS2X library.

usage:

encodels <passphrase> <message>
Responds with secret message.

decodels <passphrase> <secret>
Responds with original message.

--- Actual Example:

ssviatko@icosahedron:~/c/little-secrets$ ./encodels "Stephen Sviatko" "Hello there"
g7wu0NQZEg70ey1Jbej8hmPzC797DKYePz4pr2bshPAoSRNgJ4koTZAVaHDekcHB

ssviatko@icosahedron:~/c/little-secrets$ ./decodels "Stephen Sviatko" "g7wu0NQZEg70ey1Jbej8hmPzC797DKYePz4pr2bshPAoSRNgJ4koTZAVaHDekcHB"
Hello there

